## Summary

| Agent            | Trigger (examples)                    | Runs in Cursor |
|------------------|---------------------------------------|----------------|
| Compound review  | "run compound review", "compound learnings" | Yes — you read logs/daily-context.md and RULE.md / .cursor/rules, then update them. |
| Auto-compound    | "run auto-compound", "pick next priority"    | Yes — you read reports/priorities.md, create PRD/tasks, implement. |

These are the **agents running on Cursor**. The nightly launchd jobs (10:30 / 11:00 PM) are separate: they run scripts that use Anthropic API or AGENT_CMD when the user is not in Cursor.
